Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_fus_read_times

IFB fuses are 0 to 1791. The reset values are for IFB fuses for PLL_REF_CLK up to 100MHz when core PLL is engaged. If any of the formulas below result in a value less than zero, the corresponding timing parameter should be set to zero.

Prior to issuing a read to the fuse banks (via MIO_FUS_RCMD), this register should be written with the timing parameters that will be read. This register should not be written while MIO_FUS_RCMD[PEND] = 1.
